Your doctor has prescribed Renitec to control high blood pressure or improve your heart's performance (treatment of heart failure). Renitec is also used for the prevention of symptomatic heart failure. In many heart failure patients who have symptoms, Renitec slows the worsening of heart failure and reduces the need for hospitalization for heart failure. Renitec also helps some of these patients to live longer. In many patients with early-stage heart failure, before symptoms develop, Renitec helps to prevent weakened cardiac performance and delay the onset of symptoms (for example, shortness of breath, tiredness after light physical activities such as walking, or swelling of the ankles and feet). These patients may need fewer hospitalizations for heart failure. When taking Renitec, some patients with heart failure may be at lower risk of suffering a heart attack (myocardial infarction). "Let us be realistic, let us do the impossible." Ernesto Che Guevara (1928-1967) is an icon. Images of his face that are both severe and hopeful (based on the famous photograph taken by Cuban Alberto Korda) are widespread in the world, even ingrained in pop culture. But what is hidden behind this portrait, behind the symbol of rebellion and hope? This book proposes to answer that question, following the trajectory of the young Argentine medical student on an initiatic journey through Latin America and the man who joins a revolutionary movement, overthrows the Cuban dictator Fulgencio Batista with Fidel Castro and ends up promote a revolutionary court. Creator of the “work and re-education” camps, Che Guevara held several important positions in the Cuban government. After disappearing from national political life and fighting in Congo, the man who is credited with the phrase "it must be hardened, but without losing tenderness" was summarily executed by the Bolivian army.

With his latest album, “Setevidas”, Pitty went on a tour of the country. With a revamped show and repertoire that brought, in addition to the songs on the album, her greatest hits and some surprises, she dragged crowds wherever she went. Much of this tour is recorded on the DVD "Tour Setevidas - Ao Vivo", released by Deck. The new work brings the full show recorded at Audio Club in July 2015, which was broadcast live by Multishow. In the repertoire of the presentation are the songs from the most recent album, such as "Serpente", "Um Leão" and "Boca Aberta", and successes of his career, among them "Me Adora", "Na Sua Estante" and "Mask". And yet, there is a documentary on the tour on the DVD, directed and filmed by Otavio Sousa, lasting almost an hour. He accompanied the singer and his band, formed by Martin Mendonça (guitar), Duda Machado (drums), Gui Almeida (bass) and Paulo Kishimoto (lap steel, moog and percussion), on trips, recording excerpts from the shows and behind the scenes images ! Already in the title of this novel by Mario Vargas Llosa, published in 1977, the double story in which his argument is based is collected: on the one hand, the love relationship of the young writer Varguitas with a woman from his family older than he, the Aunt Julia; and on the other, the unbridled presence of the newsletter writer Pedro Camacho on the same radio station where Varguitas works. The noble love passion between Aunt Julia and the novelist's apprentice, which the Lima society of the fifties tries by all means to prevent, is combined in this novel by Vargas Llosa with the gruesome narratives of the wave newsletter. of a burning passion with Shakespearean airs and its melodramatic correlate and the unexpected confluence of the devotee of high literature and the creeping writer are some keys to this greater narration of Mario Vargas Llosa. Aunt Julia and the writer bring together the interest of adventure stories, where the reader's attention is subject to a continuously postponed happy ending, and the most hilarious and grotesque hobby, thanks no doubt to the amusing contributions of the writer Camacho, one of the great characters of the Peruvian novelist.

translated_title: Why? - How to Motivate People and Teams to Act
translated_description: Why are some people and organizations more innovative, more influential and more profitable than others? Why do some get greater loyalty from both customers and employees? Even among the successful ones, why are so few able to repeat success over and over again? People like Martin Luther King Jr., Steve Jobs and the Wright brothers may have little in common, but they all started with why. The natural ability to start with why has enabled them to inspire the people around them to do remarkable things. Starting with why is valid for both small and big businesses, both for the universe of non-profit entities and for politics. Whoever starts with why never manipulates, inspires. And people follow them not because they need to, but because they want to.

Eugene Simonet (Kevin Spacey) is a professor of Social Studies whose life is in the most perfect order, everything and everyone in their right places. One day he decides to ask his students for a job. Trevor (Haley Joel Osment) who is in that class proposes a kind of chain of goodness where each person would do a favor to three other people and they would do the same thing, without asking for anything in return. The favor that each person does has to be something big, something that people cannot do for themselves. With that Trevor seeks to help his own family which is summarized in his mother Alice McKinney (Helen Hunt), a courageous and hardworking woman, who has two jobs and struggles to raise her son. translated_title: Judicial Activism in the National Tax System
translated_description: The Supreme Federal Court has many precedents in which tax laws were declared unconstitutional based on concepts pre-conceived by the judge, as if the National Tax System were completely contained in the Constitution, and as if the meaning of this Constitution were the patrimony of some Power. In Brazilian Tax Law, there are special factors that strengthen this activist stance. However, the constitutional interpretation is a dynamic work of the three Powers and of the whole society, in a joint effort that never ends. In this book, some alternatives to judicial activism will be presented, such as: the theory of constitutional dialogues, judicial self-containment, the methodological plurality of interpretation, the possible marginal contents of the concepts, the recognition of the creative and decision-making role of legislative discretion, among others .

It also contains the protein keratin which is the most important component of hair. Monessa has beneficial effects in several cases of hair loss due to non-scarring. Indapen SR is a prolonged-release tablet that contains indapamide as its active ingredient. Indapamide is a diuretic. Most diuretics increase the amount of urine produced by the kidneys. Indapen SR acts in the control of blood pressure, through a vascular mechanism, with its maintenance within physiological limits. translated_title: Fiscal Policy and Economic Cycles - Theory and Rec Experience
translated_description: With the international financial crisis, interest in the effects of fiscal policy was renewed. To combat the economic depression, several fiscal incentives were adopted. In the next moment, several countries engaged in contractionary policies. Throughout these experiences, the temperature of the economic debate has risen, giving rise to controversies worthy of the historic macroeconomic disputes. The purpose of this book is to systematize the main experiences, theories and evidence on the subject. This book is structured in three main areas. The first has the objective of presenting the topic to the interested reader, documenting the relevant international experience on the subject. The documented results allow us to point out which conditions the most successful experiences occurred. The second axis develops the theoretical part and its objective is to deepen the reader's knowledge in the face of an analytical structure. In the end, it will be possible to understand the circumstances that make fiscal policy more effective in stabilizing the economy. The third axis presents the main empirical evidence available seeking to reconcile with the theory. Topics such as the expansionist contraction thesis, the relationship between debt and growth and the empirical evidence of fiscal multipliers are discussed. At the end of each of the chapters, a balance of the discussion is made so that the reader can understand the various applications of economic policy involved and their repercussions. The last chapter presents the main conclusions and gaps that still exist in the debate.

The still distilled alembic undergoes a process of smoothing the same that other whiskey of the family of Jack Daniel's pass. It Makes You Pass About Three Meters Of Maple Charcoal But In This Case It Doesn't Go A Once, But It Does A Second. With this usual procedure of the Lynchburg distillery, it is possible to soften the distillate in a very noticeable way before starting maturation in American oak barrels. Gentleman Jack passes again through the charcoal sieve once it has reached maturity in barrels. This Is The Only Whiskey In The World That Ends Its Maturity Period In The Same Way It Started: Filtered By Maple Charcoal. The result is a Tennessee Whiskey of amazing smoothness. After the years of maturity in barrels, Jack Daniel's Gentleman Jack has acquired a brilliant chestnut honey color, leaving one to think when he sees the thin tears in the glass that has a good glyceric index. The lingering finish leaves citrus sensations with hints of cinnamon, leaving us with a subtle and dry caramelized sugar aftertaste. The Label Qualifies This Jack Daniel'S Gentleman Jack As Rare Tennessee Whiskey "Rare" Because It Is The Only Whiskey In The World That Spends Two Times For Maple Charcoal Both Before And After Being Aged In Oak. Neovlar name of the active substance: Ethinylestradiol + Levonorgestrel MS 1705600620019 Neovlar is indicated for preventing pregnancy. How does Neovlar work? Neovlar is a combined oral contraceptive. Each pill contains a combination of two female hormones: levonorgestrel (progestin) and ethinyl estradiol (estrogen). Due to the small concentrations of both hormones, Neovlar is considered a low-dose oral contraceptive. Other features unrelated to pregnancy prevention Combined contraceptives reduce the duration and intensity of menstrual bleeding, decreasing the risk of iron deficiency anemia. Menstrual cramping can also become less intense or disappear completely. In addition, some disorders have been reported to occur less frequently in contraceptive users containing 0.05 mg ethinyl estradiol (“high-dose pill”), such as: benign breast disease, ovarian cysts, pelvic infections (pelvic inflammatory disease) or IPD), ectopic pregnancy (when the fetus settles outside the uterus) and cancer of the endometrium (tissue lining the uterus) and ovaries. This may also be the case for low-dose contraceptives, but so far only a reduction in the occurrence of cases of ovarian and endometrial cancer has been confirmed.

Humulin 70N / 30R name of the active substance: Human Insulin MS 1126001780013 Humulin 70N / 30R is indicated for the treatment of patients with diabetes mellitus to control the rate of glucose in the body. How does the Humulin 70N / 30R work? Insulin is a hormone produced by the pancreas (gland located near the stomach). This hormone is necessary for the use of sugar by the body. Diabetes occurs when the pancreas does not produce enough insulin to supply the body's needs. To control diabetes, your doctor prescribes insulin injections to keep your blood glucose (sugar) rate close to normal. Adequate control of diabetes requires strict and constant cooperation between the patient and the doctor. Despite diabetes, the patient can lead an active and healthy life if he or she follows a balanced daily diet, exercises regularly and takes insulin injections exactly as determined by the doctor. The diabetic should have blood glucose (blood glucose) or glycosuria (urine glucose) tests regularly. If blood tests show consistently changing glucose levels (above or below normal) or if urine tests constantly show glucose, this is a sign that diabetes is not controlled and the patient should take this fact to the next level. doctor's knowledge. Always have an extra supply of insulin and the correct delivery devices on hand. Use identification that you are diabetic, so that you can provide adequate care if any complications occur when you are away from home. The duration of action of any insulin can vary considerably in different individuals or at different times in the same individual. As with all insulin preparations, the duration of action of Humulin 70N / 30R depends on the dose, place of application, blood availability, temperature and physical activity.

Sotalol hydrochloride Sandoz name of the active substance: Sotalol hydrochloride MS 1004703250041 Sotalol hydrochloride is indicated for the treatment and control of cardiac arrhythmias, in all cases of angina pectoris (chest pain), in the post-myocardial infarction. Cardiac arrhythmia is a change in the rhythm of the heartbeat that may or may not be noticeable to the person. Angina of the heart is the pain that occurs due to tiredness of the heart muscle when the amount of blood that reaches the heart is less than it needs to beat. Myocardial infarction (or heart attack) is the death of a part of the heart muscle that occurs due to an abrupt lack of blood, leaving the heart without the nutrients and oxygen necessary for its normal functioning. After a heart attack, it is very important to decrease the load or the effort that the heart has to make to beat normally, because the muscle is healing and cannot increase its work. The above conditions can appear separately or together in a given person. How does Sotalol - Sandoz Hydrochloride work? Sotalol hydrochloride is a beta-adrenergic receptor blocking agent. Decreases nerve stimulation in some organs such as the heart, kidneys and lungs. Its use improves the heart's rhythm, as it reduces the speed and strength of beats, decreasing the need for oxygen and facilitating contractions. Sotalol hydrochloride also acts on the kidneys by decreasing the mechanism that retains salt and water for the body, which also helps to improve the functioning of the heart. Its action starts a few hours after the first dose and becomes constant after 2 to 3 days of use.

Warnings: The use of excessive doses or long-term treatment with Budecort® Aqua may lead to the appearance of signs or symptoms of hypercorticism (excessive release of hormones from the adrenal cortex), suppression of the hypothalamus-pituitary-adrenal function and / or Growth Inhibition In Children. Contraindications: Budecort® Aqua should not be used by patients with allergies to Budesonide or any component of the formula. Cautions and warnings: The long-term effects of Budecort® Aqua on children are not fully known. The physician should closely monitor the growth of children receiving long-term Budecort® Aqua by any route and evaluate the benefits of treating Budecort® Aqua and the possibility of growth inhibition. The presence of liver problems can affect the elimination of Budecort® Aqua from the organism. However, this fact is of limited clinical importance for Budecort® Aqua. Tell your doctor if you have other health problems, especially if you have or have had tuberculosis or liver problems. Budecort® Aqua does not interfere with the ability to drive vehicles and operate machinery. This medication should not be used by pregnant women without medical advice or a dental surgeon. There is no evidence that Budecort® Aqua is harmful when used by pregnant women or while breastfeeding. Children should only use Budecort® Aqua under adult supervision to ensure that the dose is correctly administered and in accordance with the doctor's prescription. Warning: This medication contains sugar (47.50 mg / ml of anhydrous glucose), therefore, it should be used with caution and at the discretion of the doctor in patients with diabetes. translated_title: How to Sew a Button and Other Useful Things Your Grandma Knows Does
translated_description: How to sew a button is a celebration of authenticity and self-confidence. The journalist Erin Bried gathered more than 100 essential tips on beauty, cooking, tidiness, gardening, fun and other everyday topics, which free women, and why not men, from the bonds of dependence. These are practices that rescue “do it yourself” and give more originality to everyday life and even to special occasions. Currently, everyone is dependent on several service chains: laundries pass the shirts, delivery men bring the pizza, florists make flower arrangements. The pace imposed by modern life means that people have little or no time to care for themselves and the people they love. In rescuing the teachings of our grandmothers combined with the opinion of some experts, the author not only reveals knowledge lost in time, but also gives valuable ideas for a life with less expenses. “If you no longer have your grandmother around, I hope this book will bring her spirit close to you, offering you a warm stimulus and gently guiding you through the essential tasks of life that you may have forgotten or never learned. I hope this brings you calm, well-being and, above all, self-confidence ”, wishes the author. The knowledge shared by the author please has the power to revolutionize a lifestyle or only assist in the most common tasks. Learning how to plant a mini garden in a small space can be very useful. Eliminating mold is among those simple tasks, but nobody knows how to do it. Erin Bried goes on to explain how to prepare (and preserve) fruit jelly, how to do her nails herself, how to control her budget and even how to prepare her own beer. These and other gems of the wisdom of a not-so-distant past, but which seems remote, can simplify everyday life and give life more originality and charm. "With this book, every woman will feel as if she is sitting on her grandmother's lap, acquiring the knowledge we need to be smarter, happier and become better people. Good reading!" Lucy Danziger, editor in chief of SELF magazine "Alegre, fun and emancipatory. With refined humor, Erin Bried gives really useful tips for everyday tasks. At the end of 1983 Renato Russo, Dado Villa-Lobos and Marcelo Bonfá were invited to record a demo at EMI-Odeon. They were sure that their time had come as it had arrived for the Paralamas do Sucesso a year earlier. The band entered the studios of the Rio de Janeiro branch of the Beatles' label and recorded 3 songs: “It's still early”, “Geração Coca-Cola and“ A Dança ”, the latter with the participation of the friend Herbert Vianna. It didn't work and the band returned to Brasilia. These 3 recordings were never used. The band would return to Rio the following year to rehearse and record these songs again on the first album that bears the band's name: “Legião Urbana”, one of the biggest hits of national rock of the 80's. Both these 3 demos and all the recordings of the rehearsals were kept until today in the label's collection. Last year the album completed 3 decades and to commemorate this date, the commemorative edition of this album renamed Legião Urbana 30 anos is launched. This edition is double with the first original CD with the 11 tracks digitally remastered and a second CD with 18 unpublished recordings: There are 7 Outtakes, that is, recordings different from those used on the original CD, 2 remixes (one by Mario Caldato and one de Liminha), the 3 demos of 1983, we recorded in Brasília, a "pirate" recording of "Química", two sensational statements by Renato Russo, and etc ... And in the graphic part besides having a double digipak luxury packaging , a new booklet was created full of fanzines and clippings of the time with unpublished photos. A material rich in sound and visual. Now it is to embark and enjoy the new versions of the greatest hits of national Rock of all times as “Geração-Cola” with a much heavier footprint, “It’s still early” with English lyrics by Renato, and many, many surprises. Desalex name of the active substance: Desloratadine MS 1002901910017 Desalex is indicated for the relief of symptoms associated with allergic rhinitis, such as: runny nose (runny nose), sneezing and itchy nose (itchy nose), burning and itchy eyes (itchy eyes), watery, itchy palate (itchy palate) and cough. Eye and nasal signs and symptoms are quickly relieved after oral administration of the product. Desalex is also indicated for the relief of signs and symptoms of hives and other skin allergies. How does Desalex work? Desalex prevents histamine (the substance causing the allergy) from acting (prevents its release, blocks its action at the allergy site and prevents inflammation due to the allergic response) and thus combats the symptoms of intermittent and persistent allergic rhinitis, urticaria and other allergies. Desalex does not cause drowsiness.

Janumet name of the active substance: Sitagliptin phosphate + Metformin hydrochloride MS 1002901770045 Your doctor has prescribed Janumet to help reduce your blood sugar levels. Janumet should be combined with a diet and exercise program recommended by your doctor. What is type 2 diabetes? Type 2 diabetes is a condition in which your body does not produce enough insulin, and the insulin produced does not work as well as it should. Your body can also produce a lot of sugar. When this occurs, blood sugar (glucose) rises and can cause health problems. The main purpose of treating diabetes is to normalize blood sugar levels. Reducing and controlling blood sugar levels can help prevent or delay complications of diabetes, such as heart disease, kidney disease, loss of vision and limb amputation. High blood sugar levels can be reduced through diet and exercise and with the use of some medications. How does Janumet work? Janumet is a pill that contains two drugs, sitagliptin phosphate and metformin, which lower blood sugar. Sitagliptin phosphate belongs to a class of medicines called DPP-4 inhibitors (dipeptidyl peptidase-4 inhibitors) and metformin hydrochloride is a member of the biguanide class. These two components work together to control blood sugar levels in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus. Type 2 diabetes was called non-insulin-dependent diabetes mellitus. Janumet lowers blood sugar levels in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus. Janumet helps to improve insulin levels after a meal. Janumet helps the body to respond better to insulin. Janumet decreases the amount of sugar produced by the body. It is unusual for Janumet to cause low blood sugar levels (hypoglycaemia).

MS 1057303690088 Fisioton is indicated in situations where there is an excessive physical and / or mental demand resulting in symptoms of fatigue, tiredness, decreased work performance, reduced mental and reflex agility and also decreased performance and the ability to perform physical exercises. These symptoms, which have various causes, can result in impairment of the individual's quality of life, interfering with their good physical and mental performance and decreasing performance in their activities. The use of Fisioton helps to attenuate these symptoms and to restore the individual's physical and mental conditions. How does Fisioton work? Fisioton is a medicine of plant origin derived from the extract of the plant called Rhodiola rosea L., obtained through a rigorous method of cultivation and extraction, guaranteeing its quality and the absence of toxic substances in its composition. Rhodiola rosea L. is traditionally used in several European countries with the aim of reducing fatigue and contributing to increase the capacity for physical and mental work, providing a better balance of the organism to adapt to situations that cause greater wear such as, exercises intense physics, work overload, excessive mental activity and night work, adjusting the body's level of response to these factors.

Biotônico Fontoura N name of the active substance: Ferrous Sulphate Heptahydrate + Phosphoric Acid MS 1781700400016 Biotônico Fontoura N is a mineral supplement indicated as an aid in needy anemias and in inadequate diets. How does Biotônico Fontoura N work? Biotônico Fontoura N is an oral medication composed of substances that provide iron and phosphorus, which are important to help in the treatment of iron deficiency anemia (lack of iron). Iron is a constituent element of hemoglobins (blood cells) that are responsible for the transport of oxygen in living beings. Phosphorus is a mineral necessary to activate the action of essential vitamins, such as some of the B complex. The main criteria for a good response to oral iron treatment are: Reduction or disappearance of symptoms and signs related to iron deficiency; Greater tolerance to physical activity; Reticulocytosis (increase in reticulocytes in the blood that are the precursors of erythrocytes (red blood cells = hemoglobin), which can already be seen between the 3rd and 5th day of the start of treatment and is maximum between the 8th and 10th day; Hb (hemoglobin) of at least 2 g / dL after two to three weeks of treatment.

A new job seems to be the turning point for Rick: chase six runaway androids and retire them. Elixir Paregoric name of the active substance: Tincture of Opium MS Exempt Elixir Paregoric is indicated as antispasmodic, against gas, stomach pain and intestinal pain. How does Paregoric Elixir work? Opium (which in Greek means “juice”) is a dry extract obtained from the plant Papaver somniferum L. (Papaverácea). The camphor tincture of opium or Elixir Paregorico is a pharmaceutical preparation described in Pharmacopoeias. The word paregoric is derived from the Greek and means "calming" and in fact can be used for gastrointestinal disorders such as abdominal pain. Studies confirm the analgesic and antispasmodic effects of this medication. The average time of onset of action of the drug will depend on the conditions of each organism.

Domperidone Compridido Eurofarma name of the active substance: Domperidone MS 1004311630039 This medicine is intended for the treatment of: Dyspeptic syndromes often associated with delayed gastric emptying, gastroesophageal reflux and esophagitis; Sensation of epigastric bundling, early satiety, abdominal distension, upper abdominal pain; Eructation, flatulence; Nausea and vomiting; Heartburn, epigastric burning with or without gastric content regurgitation; Nausea and vomiting of functional, organic, infectious or alimentary origin or induced by radiotherapy or drug treatment (anti-inflammatory, antineoplastic). A specific indication is the nausea and vomiting induced by dopaminergic agonists used in the treatment of Parkinson's disease such as L- dopa and bromocriptine. How does Domperidona Comprimido - Eurofarma work? Domperidone is a medicine that makes the movement of food through the esophagus, stomach and intestines faster, in such a way that the food is not stopped for a long time in the same place, or there is reflux of it. Symptom control is observed progressively over the course of treatment.

Ansentron name of the active substance: Ondansetron Hydrochloride Dihydrate MS 1121301570041 Ansentron is indicated for use in adults and children from 6 months of age for the control of nausea and vomiting that are caused by some treatments, such as chemotherapy or radiation therapy, avoiding as soon as you feel sick, sick or vomit after these treatments. It is also indicated for the prevention of nausea and vomiting after an operation, in adults and children from 1 month of age. How does Ansentron work? Certain medical treatments, such as chemotherapy, radiation and surgery, can cause your body to release serotonin, a substance that causes nausea and vomiting. Ansentron belongs to a group of medicines called antiemetics and blocks the action of this substance, thus preventing you from feeling nausea and vomiting from these treatments. Injectable Ansentron has a rapid onset of action, which is why it can be used to induce anesthesia or immediately before chemotherapy or radiation therapy, as appropriate.

translated_description: In this bold work, Harvard economist Seth Stephens-Davidowitz argues that much of what we thought about people was completely wrong. The reason? Everyone lies, to friends, partners, doctors, research - and to himself. However, we no longer need to trust what people tell us. New data from the internet finally reveals the truth. By analyzing this digital gold mine, we can now discover what people really think, want and do. Todo Mundo Mente combines the informed analysis of Nate Silver's The Sign and the Noise, the Outstanding Storytelling - Outliers, by Malcolm Gladwell, and the wit and fun of Freakonomics, by Steven Levitt and Stephen Dubner, in a book that will change the way you look at the world. The ability to learn about human nature from Big Data is virtually limitless - just ask the right questions. “An incredibly intelligent and malicious exploration of what Big Data tells us about everyday life. Seth Stephens Davidowtiz is the best storyteller with data I have ever known. ”- Steven Levitt, co-author of Freakonomics“ Forget Freakonomics. Forget Moneyball. This brilliant book is the best demonstration of how big data combined with intelligence can illuminate and change the world. According to the law, elementary and high schools will have to introduce in their program content "the study of the history of Africa and Africans, the struggle of blacks in Brazil, black Brazilian culture and blacks in the formation of national society, rescuing the contribution of the black people in the social, economic and political areas relevant to the history of Brazil ". Vivacor name of the active substance: Rosuvastatin Calcic MS 1161801980171 Vivacor should be used as an aid to diet when the response to diet and exercise is inadequate. In adult patients with hypercholesterolemia (high blood cholesterol level) Vivacor is indicated for: Reduction of LDL-cholesterol levels, total cholesterol and elevated triglycerides; increased HDLcholesterol in patients with primary hypercholesterolemia (heterozygous and unfamiliar familial) and mixed dyslipidemia (elevated or abnormal blood lipid levels) (Fredrickson types IIa and IIb). Vivacor also decreases ApoB, non-HDL-C, VLDL-C, VLDL-TG, and LDLC / HDL-C, total C / HDL-C, non-HDL-C / HDL-C, ApoB / ApoA- I and increases ApoA-I in these populations; Treatment of isolated hypertriglyceridemia (high blood triglyceride level) (Fredrickson type IV hyperlipidemia); Reduction of total cholesterol and LDL-C in patients with homozygous familial hypercholesterolemia, either alone or as an adjunct to diet and other lipid-lowering treatments (eg LDL apheresis), if such treatments are not sufficient; Slowing or reducing the progression of atherosclerosis (accumulation of fat on the walls of blood vessels). Children and adolescents from 10 to 17 years of age: Vivacor is indicated for the reduction of total cholesterol, LDL-C and ApoB in patients with familial heterozygous hypercholesterolemia (HeFH). How does Vivacor work? Rosuvastatin, Vivacor's active ingredient, inhibits an enzyme important for the production of cholesterol by the body, called HMG-CoA reductase, therefore, the continuous use of Vivacor reduces the level of lipids (fatty substances) in the blood, mainly cholesterol and triglycerides. This reduction is usually achieved within 4 weeks and is continued after treatment.

Considered one of the masterpieces of Sociology, this classic study by Durkheim presents suicide as a phenomenon whose origins are grounded in society itself. However, without abandoning the influence exerted by the psychological factor, the author proposes a break with the understanding that this is the principle that primarily triggers and generates influence in the production of the act, and demonstrates that it is possible to study and understand it more broadly. from the understanding of the society itself, its structure and all the determinations previously imposed on the individual by that institution. Among the preponderant factors for suicide, Durkheim carefully analyzes marital status, religious option and social integration, and characterizes it in three essential types: selfish, altruistic and anomic. In this work, the author vehemently defends the sociological character inherent in suicide, interpreting it as a tendency already present in society, to which the individual, far from his central point of balance, ends up succumbing, bringing it to manifestation.

Tantin name of the active substance: Gestodene + Ethinylestradiol MS 1097401420025 Tantin (gestodene + ethinylestradiol) is indicated for the prevention of pregnancy. Although well established, there are cases of pregnancy in women using oral contraceptives. How does Tantin work? Tantin is an oral contraceptive that combines 2 hormones, ethinyl estradiol and gestodene. Combined oral contraceptives, which have 2 hormones in their composition, act by suppressing gonadotropins, that is, by inhibiting hormonal stimuli that lead to ovulation. Although the primary result of this action is inhibition of ovulation, other changes include changes in the cervical mucus (which increases the difficulty of sperm entering the uterus) and in the endometrium (which reduces the likelihood of implantation in the endometrium).

Dorilax name of the active substance: Caffeine + Carisoprodol + Paracetamol MS 1057300210018 This medicine is intended for the treatment of painful, rheumatic or traumatic conditions, such as: Muscle pain; Spasms (contractions); Muscle strain (rupture of muscle fibers); Trauma of unspecified body region (blunt injury that causes pain and swelling); Torticollis (stiffening of the neck muscles causing pain); Dislocation (displacement of one or more bones in a joint); Sprain (joint injury in which there was no dislocation); Distension of unspecified body region (injury to tendon, muscle or ligament near a joint). How does Dorilax work? Dorilax presents in its composition substances with muscle relaxing and analgesic activity. Paracetamol has analgesic (against pain) and antipyretic (against fever) action. Carisoprodol is a muscle relaxant that indirectly reduces muscle tension in humans. Caffeine is a stimulant of the central nervous system, which acts on the musculature, making it less susceptible to fatigue (tiredness) and improving its performance. Caffeine produces a state of mental alertness and tends to correct the sleepiness that carisoprodol causes. The estimated average time to start the action after you take Dorilax is 15 to 45 minutes.

Orlipid name of the active substance: Orlistate MS 1356906490030 Orlipid is indicated for the treatment of overweight or obese patients, including patients with risk factors associated with obesity, in conjunction with a low calorie diet. Orlipid is effective in long-term weight control (weight loss, weight maintenance and preventing the recovery of lost weight). Orlipid improves risk factors associated with being overweight, such as hypercholesterolemia (high blood cholesterol), glucose intolerance (“pre-diabetes”), type 2 diabetes, hyperinsulinemia, (high blood insulin) high blood pressure (high blood pressure) ), and also promotes the reduction of visceral fat (located between the abdominal organs). It can also be used to treat overweight or obese type 2 diabetes patients. Orlipid, in conjunction with a low-calorie diet and oral antidiabetic drugs and / or insulin, promotes additional blood sugar control. How does Orlipid work? Orlipid acts directly on the digestive system, preventing about 30% of the fat you eat with food from being absorbed at each meal, and this excess is eliminated with the stool. Therefore, your body will stop storing a good amount of fats per meal, helping you to reduce your weight. In addition, it will help to prevent new weight gain, reducing the risks of diabetes, hypertension and increased cholesterol. The effect of Orlipid can be seen in 24 to 48 hours after its administration. Weight loss and the benefits of using Orlipid generally begin within the first two weeks of treatment.

Hypertil active substance name: Manidipine dihydrochloride + Delapril hydrochloride MS 1005801060016 Hypertil is indicated for the treatment of high blood pressure. Combination therapy is also indicated when an additional reduction in blood pressure is required, compared to therapy using just delapril or manidipine. How does Hypertil work? Hypertil has antihypertensive activity by two agents, an inhibitor of the angiotensin converting enzyme (delapril hydrochloride) and a calcium channel antagonist (manidipine dihydrochloride). Angiotensin II is a substance produced in our body that causes narrowing of blood vessels and a consequent increase in blood pressure. Delapril inhibits the production of angiotensin II, causing a reduction in blood pressure. Manidipine belongs to a group of drugs called calcium channel antagonists, which blocks the flow of calcium to the smooth muscle cells of blood vessels, causing relaxation of the muscle fibers of the blood vessels, with a consequent reduction in blood pressure. In general, complete antihypertensive activity is seen between the fourth and sixth week of treatment.

Rosamunde Pilcher's great family saga, Os Shell Collectors, launched in 1987 in Europe and in 1990 by Bertrand Brasil, is gaining a new look. In homage to the 30th edition in Brazil of this beloved novel, Rosamunde Pilcher wrote an introduction that tells the story of the genesis of this work. The book is a romance of bonds - from one generation to the next; the parents who are still alive; and the symbols and legacies of the past that come to represent the future. It deals with the search for identity in the fragmented mirror of our childhood and the confrontation with the image blurred by the emergence of memories from the past. The novel is full of real people and steeped in everyday values; Rosamunde Pilcher's characters could be any of us. The reader is invited to share the joy, sadness and magic of the book. Setting the scene in London and Cornwall, from the Second World War to the present day, Rosamunde Pilcher tells the story of the Keeling family, and the passions and disappointments that have kept it together for three generations. The family gravitates around Penélope, and it is their love, courage and ethical sense that determine the course of all their lives. Among the goods that are most dear to Penelope is The shell collectors, which her father painted and gave her. left as a souvenir and legacy. It is this painting that symbolizes the links between the generations - the present, the past and the future. But it is precisely the fate of this painting that may come to disaggregate the family ... Writing with great compassion for the weaknesses, desires and human joys, the story of Rosamunde Pilcher overflows with emotion. The world she created and opened up for us becomes a place where we feel at ease, a place we can hardly wait to return to, a place we will never forget.

translated_title: Anlodipine Besylate 5 mg Generic Sandoz with 30 Tablets
translated_description: Anlodipino Besylate Sandoz name of the active substance: Anlodipino Besylate MS 1004705570027 Anlodipino Besylate is indicated as a drug of first choice in the treatment of hypertension (high blood pressure) and angina pectoris (chest pain, due to heart disease) due to ischemia myocardial (lack of blood in the heart). Anlodipine Besylate can be used alone or in combination with other medications to treat the same indications above. How does Anlodipino - Sandoz Besylate work? Amlodipine, the active ingredient in the medication of Anlodipine Besylate, interferes with the movement of calcium into the heart cells and the blood vessel muscles. As a result of this action, the amlodipine relaxes the blood vessels that irrigate the heart and the rest of the body, increasing the amount of blood and oxygen to the heart, reducing its workload and, by relaxing the blood vessels, allows the blood pass through them more easily. High blood pressure imposes an overload on the heart and arteries (blood vessels) that, in the long run, makes the heart and arteries not function properly. This can cause damage to the blood vessels in the brain, heart and kidneys, resulting in strokes (strokes), heart and kidney failure (changes in heart and kidney function). High blood pressure can also increase the risk of a heart attack (heart attack). If blood pressure is controlled, these problems may not occur or there is less chance that they will occur.
